25/06/2010
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- European Integration Minister Gordana Djurovic says Montenegro will be prepared to join the EU by 2014.
She announced on Thursday (June 24th) that the government adopted a new four-year communication strategy for EU membership, targetting groups that will be subject to the information strategy during integration preparations.
Djurovic noted that both NGOs and the European Commission provided suggestions.
(RTCG, Pcnen, B92, Beta - 24/06/10)
